defaultPlace-based finance that provides areas with greater control over their tax, spending and borrowing
default,
default allowing a stronger focus on the needs of both local people and the local economy;
default11.2.
default 
defaultFair, transparent and certain distribution of local gov
defaulternment finance led by local government, which could be extended to the funding for other public services;
