defaultFive year funding settlements for local public services
default,
default providing certainty and the basis for greater service integration, early intervention and in
defaultvestment in growth;
default11.4.
default 
defaultScrapping the Barnett Formula for allocating funding to the devolved nations, and investing in preventative public services that reduce demand on
default,
default more expensive
default,
default acute services.
